## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

### Primary Objective
Create a 2.5D animation application from scratch to finish using a custom Domain-Specific Language (DSL) with real-time preview and multi-format video export capabilities.

### Core Features
1. **Custom DSL Animation Engine** - Frame-based keyframe animation system with smooth interpolation
2. **AI-Assisted DSL Generation** - Users describe animations; external AI generates DSL code
3. **Real-Time Canvas Preview** - 360p @ 12fps interactive preview with timeline scrubbing
4. **Advanced Effects System** - 30+ professional animation effects (blur, glow, color grading, etc.)
5. **Project Management** - Create, save, rename, duplicate, delete projects with auto-save
6. **Multi-Format Export** - MP4, MKV, GIF at 1080p/2K/4K @ 30fps/60fps
7. **Offline-First Architecture** - All features work offline (except AI DSL generation)
8. **Text Animation** - Full 3D animated text with bundled OTF fonts

### User Type
Single user (developer/animator personal tool) - Sole user optimization

