## 2. TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE

### Tech Stack
- **Language:** Kotlin
- **Platform:** Android Studio (Gradle-based)
- **Graphics Engine:** OpenGL ES 3.0 (Canvas rendering)
- **Video Encoding:** FFmpeg via ffmpeg-kit-android
- **Storage:** SQLite (project metadata) + File system (.codm format)
- **Persistence:** SharedPreferences + Room Database
- **UI Framework:** Jetpack Compose + Traditional Android Views (hybrid)
- **Animation Core:** Custom keyframe interpolator with easing functions
- **Minimum API:** 29 (Android 10)
- **Target API:** 34 (Android 14)

### Architecture Pattern
- **MVVM** (Model-View-ViewModel)
- **Repository Pattern** for data access
- **Dependency Injection** via Hilt
- **Coroutines** for async operations

