## 4. DATA MODELS

### Project Structure (.codm File)
```json
{
  "version": "1.0",
  "projectName": "MyAnimation",
  "createdAt": "2026-06-13T10:30:00Z",
  "modifiedAt": "2026-06-13T10:35:00Z",
  "canvasWidth": 1920,
  "canvasHeight": 1080,
  "fps": 30,
  "duration": 120000,
  "dslCode": "[full DSL code here]",
  "thumbnail": "[base64 image data]",
  "metadata": {
    "exportFormats": ["mp4", "mkv", "gif"],
    "lastExportSettings": {}
  }
}
```

### Animation Frame Object
```
AnimationFrame {
  frameNumber: Int
  timestamp: Long (milliseconds)
  objects: List<AnimatedObject>
  effects: List<AnimationEffect>
}
```

### Animated Object
```
AnimatedObject {
  id: String (UUID)
  type: String (circle, rectangle, text, etc.)
  properties: Map<String, Any>
  keyframes: List<Keyframe>
  effects: List<AnimationEffect>
  zIndex: Int
}
```

### Keyframe
```
Keyframe {
  frameNumber: Int
  properties: Map<String, Any>
  easing: EasingFunction
}
```

### Animation Effect
```
AnimationEffect {
  id: String (UUID)
  type: String (opacity, blur, rotation_3d, etc.)
  parameters: Map<String, Any>
  startFrame: Int
  endFrame: Int
  easing: EasingFunction
}
```

