### Screen 2: Editor Mode
**Purpose:** Main animation creation and DSL editing interface

**Layout Zones:**
1. **Top Bar (Fixed):**
   - Left: "Back to Home" button (auto-saves with "untitled_[timestamp]" if new)
   - Center: Project name (editable)
   - Right: Hamburger menu (Settings, Export, About)

2. **Canvas Area (60% height):**
   - OpenGL ES rendered canvas
   - Display animated objects at 360p @ 12fps
   - Interactive: Pinch zoom, Pan, Tap to select

3. **Timeline Bar (Bottom 15% of canvas area):**
   - Horizontal scrollable timeline
   - Playhead, Keyframe markers, Play/Pause/Stop buttons
   - Speed controls, Current frame indicator

4. **DSL Editor (40% height, bottom panel):**
   - Text editor with syntax highlighting
   - Line numbers, Undo/Redo, Auto-format, Error messages

5. **Right Sidebar (15% width, collapsible):**
   - Object properties panel
   - Effect controls
   - Keyframe editor
   - Layers panel

**Functionality:**
- Auto-save every 2 seconds after DSL modification
- Real-time canvas preview updates (debounced)
- DSL syntax validation
- Timeline interaction with frame scrubbing
- Canvas interaction with object selection

